<div class="board" style="width:30em;left:29em;top:0em;">
<b>Xiao, Huiyong</b> <br><br> Obtained his Ph.D. from <br><a href="http://www.cs.uic.edu">Department of Computer Science</a>,<br><a href="http://www.uic.edu">University of Illinois, Chicago</a>, the Fall of 2006. <br><br>Before then, he had been working as a Research<br> Assistant of <a href="http://www.cs.uic.edu/~ifc">Professor Isabel F. Cruz</a> in <br><a href="http://www.cs.uic.edu/~ifc/advis.html">the ADVIS Lab</a> since 2002. <br><br>His research interests generally include Semantic Web, Data Integration and Interoperability, Peer to Peer Systems, Software Engineering, Data Mining, and Information Retrieval. [<a href="mailto://hxiao@cs.uic.edu?subject=CV request&body=Can you please send me a copy of your CV?">CV</a>]<br><br>

<b>PhD thesis</b> (defended at 08/15/2006)<B>:</B><br> Query Processing For Heterogeneous Data Integration Using Ontologies. [<a href="phdthesis.pdf">download</a>]<br><br><br><b>Email address:</b> <img align="middle" src="email.gif"><br>
